Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.00,0:00:10.51,Default3,,0,0,0,,今天的告白 竟然被接受了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.30,0:00:14.13,Default3,,0,0,0,,可以啊 我们交往吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.30,0:00:18.64,Default3,,0,0,0,,总有些无法释然呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.97,0:00:23.73,Default3,,0,0,0,,那种巨乳又可爱的辣妹怎么可能会和我交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.94,0:00:25.56,Default3,,0,0,0,,用常识思考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.35,0:00:29.11,Default3,,0,0,0,,反正是先让我放松警惕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.11,0:00:31.94,Default3,,0,0,0,,然后把我的丑态散布到全校让我成为众矢之的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.49,0:00:36.20,Default3,,0,0,0,,你这么多疑可不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.49,0:00:39.08,Default3,,0,0,0,,你为什么不能相信八女同学呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.08,0:00:41.83,Default3,,0,0,0,,我们现在可是八女同学的男朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.45,0:00:45.12,Default3,,0,0,0,,你在说些什么纯情又蠢的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.46,0:00:47.42,Default3,,0,0,0,,辣妹可是很可怕的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.42,0:00:51.59,Default3,,0,0,0,,本来就是和我们不同的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.59,0:00:55.93,Default3,,0,0,0,,就是有那种思想我们才是童贞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.09,0:00:59.43,Default3,,0,0,0,,我已经受够你的漂亮话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.09,0:01:00.50,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}暴力反对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.49,0:01:17.70,Default3,,0,0,0,,不要说麻烦的话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.95,0:01:22.24,Default3,,0,0,0,,重要的只要能和那个色色的辣妹睡就好了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.83,0:01:27.08,Default3,,0,0,0,,感觉真是奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.62,0:01:30.17,Default3,,0,0,0,,刚才还认真的听课来着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.63,0:01:32.67,Default3,,0,0,0,,这样不好吧 八女同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.67,0:01:34.17,Default3,,0,0,0,,在这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.01,0:01:36.47,Default3,,0,0,0,,不好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.01,0:01:39.26,Default3,,0,0,0,,接下来不就是要做「不好」的事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.51,0:01:41.68,Default3,,0,0,0,,不 不好的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.22,0:01:44.89,Default3,,0,0,0,,真是啰嗦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.77,0:01:52.57,Default3,,0,0,0,,不好的事 等我们做完再去想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.40,0:01:54.98,Default3,,0,0,0,,等做完再想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.24,0:01:57.07,Default3,,0,0,0,,啊 好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.00,0:03:42.30,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(880,640)\fad(300,300)}第2话  第一次的卡拉OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.30,0:03:42.59,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an1}虽然昨晚的妄想里很顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.72,0:03:45.05,Default3,,0,0,0,,但是实际上到底该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.43,0:03:50.02,Default3,,0,0,0,,说实话我完全没有在和那么可爱的辣妹交往的实感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.27,0:03:52.52,Default3,,0,0,0,,再说在告白的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.98,0:03:55.90,Default3,,0,0,0,,她也是那么开心的在欺负我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.98,0:04:00.57,Default3,,0,0,0,,果然还是不要再和她扯上关系比较好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.65,0:04:01.19,Default3,,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.90,0:04:02.70,Default3,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.78,0:04:04.91,Default3,,0,0,0,,什么啊 是你们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.28,0:04:07.83,Default3,,0,0,0,,昨天的事该怎么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.83,0:04:09.62,Default3,,0,0,0,,不好意思了 纯一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.25,0:04:12.29,Default3,,0,0,0,,我们做的有些过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.79,0:04:18.84,Default3,,0,0,0,,说起来是这群家伙逼我去告白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.09,0:04:20.63,Default3,,0,0,0,,先不管那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.63,0:04:21.76,Default3,,0,0,0,,昨天怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.76,0:04:24.43,Default3,,0,0,0,,反正是被那个辣妹做了很过分的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.68,0:04:25.97,Default3,,0,0,0,,我会给你建议的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.43,0:04:31.02,Default3,,0,0,0,,其实因为昨天的事被八女同学盯上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.35,0:04:34.23,Default3,,0,0,0,,我的高中生活要被搞的乱七八糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.10,0:04:35.85,Default3,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.19,0:04:37.56,Default3,,0,0,0,,竟然这么惨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.86,0:04:40.82,Default3,,0,0,0,,我这之后要怎么办才好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.65,0:04:42.99,Default3,,0,0,0,,不要担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.82,0:04:48.24,Default3,,0,0,0,,不管你被那个辣妹传出什么传闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.41,0:04:51.74,Default3,,0,0,0,,不管你被那群现充做了多么过分的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.00,0:04:55.16,Default3,,0,0,0,,我们都会帮助纯一的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.33,0:04:58.75,Default3,,0,0,0,,因为我们永远是朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.96,0:05:00.92,Default3,,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.50,0:05:04.97,Default3,,0,0,0,,对啊 我不是还有这群家伙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.47,Default3,,0,0,0,,没有必要伤心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.89,0:05:10.14,Default3,,0,0,0,,女人已经够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.85,0:05:13.39,Default3,,0,0,0,,抱歉 有个信息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.90,Default3,,0,0,0,,自拍照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.19,0:05:22.11,Default3,,0,0,0,,说起来 昨天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.44,0:05:23.40,Default3,,0,0,0,,手机借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.40,0:05:24.19,Default3,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.36,0:05:28.03,Default3,,0,0,0,,给 这是我的联络方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.74,0:05:33.62,Default3,,0,0,0,,真是伤脑筋 擅自被交换联络方式了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.79,0:05:35.41,Default3,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.60,0:05:51.50,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(828,304)\fad(300,0)}非现充
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.85,0:05:51.50,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1099,186)\fad(300,0)}没朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.80,0:05:51.50,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(164,186)\fad(300,0)}宅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.05,0:05:51.50,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(364,641)\fad(300,0)}童贞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.54,0:05:36.75,Default3,,0,0,0,,您是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.75,0:05:39.13,Default3,,0,0,0,,现充会传染的 能别和我们说话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.17,0:05:41.67,Default3,,0,0,0,,和你这种幸福混蛋根本就不是朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.67,0:05:42.55,Default3,,0,0,0,,不如说我恨你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.55,0:05:44.92,Default3,,0,0,0,,对这种不合理的事 我都快气疯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.30,0:05:47.05,Default3,,0,0,0,,八女同学有妹妹吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.05,0:05:51.47,Default3,,0,0,0,,我不奢侈的 有小学四年级到五年级就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.06,0:05:55.06,Default3,,0,0,0,,你们的手掌翻的真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.18,0:05:56.93,Default3,,0,0,0,,手腕真柔软呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.14,0:05:58.48,Default3,,0,0,0,,你这个叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.60,0:06:00.10,Default3,,0,0,0,,真是白担心你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.52,0:06:05.74,Default3,,0,0,0,,等一下啊...并不是你们想的那样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.99,0:06:07.36,Default3,,0,0,0,,那我问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.90,0:06:10.16,Default3,,0,0,0,,已经接吻了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.32,0:06:13.74,Default3,,0,0,0,,这才一天啊 怎么可能嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.74,0:06:14.20,Default3,,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.04,0:06:17.41,Default3,,0,0,0,,听好了 纯一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.58,0:06:20.21,Default3,,0,0,0,,对辣妹而言接吻只不过是打招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.46,0:06:22.34,Default3,,0,0,0,,如果是关系好的男生的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.34,0:06:25.96,Default3,,0,0,0,,接吻就如同呼吸一般平常的东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.46,0:06:27.55,Default3,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.84,0:06:30.09,Default3,,0,0,0,,话说回来 接吻是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.09,0:06:31.97,Default3,,0,0,0,,小孩子会不会喜欢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.97,Default3,,0,0,0,,确实如此 毕竟八女同学是个辣妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.10,0:06:37.18,Default3,,0,0,0,,接吻的难度应该会下降很多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.35,0:06:40.73,Default3,,0,0,0,,而且 假设说那个回复是真的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.02,0:06:45.40,Default3,,0,0,0,,睡得好吗 纯一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.44,Default3,,0,0,0,,八...八女同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.24,0:06:49.95,Default3,,0,0,0,,这是早安的吻哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.32,0:06:55.70,Default3,,0,0,0,,也就是说我接下来可以吻到爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.70,0:06:57.25,Default3,,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.54,0:07:00.00,Default3,,0,0,0,,看来你已经明白了呢 纯一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.25,0:07:03.29,Default3,,0,0,0,,但是啊 凡事都有个先后顺序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.46,0:07:06.80,Default3,,0,0,0,,终究还是要循序渐进才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.88,0:07:08.51,Default3,,0,0,0,,明白了 师父大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.38,0:07:11.47,Default3,,0,0,0,,那我就传授你精髓所在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.39,0:07:19.48,Default3,,0,0,0,,纯一啊 邀请她去卡拉OK吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.06,0:07:23.40,Default3,,0,0,0,,那个...为什么是卡拉OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.31,0:07:30.11,Default3,,0,0,0,,你们这群童贞啊 所以说你们才一直是童贞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.11,0:07:31.11,Default3,,0,0,0,,你丫也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.11,0:07:32.66,Default3,,0,0,0,,听好了童贞们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.99,0:07:37.45,Default3,,0,0,0,,现充们是会把卡拉OK当成宾馆用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.25,Default3,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.66,0:07:44.88,Default3,,0,0,0,,这是从卡拉OK打工的经验中得到的准确情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.13,0:07:49.67,Default3,,0,0,0,,然后我从中发现了堪比诺贝尔奖的法则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.05,0:07:51.01,Default3,,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.97,0:08:00.77,Default3,,0,0,0,,卡拉OK的xx法则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.77,0:08:04.52,Default3,,0,0,0,,卡拉OK的xx法则...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.27,0:08:07.44,Default3,,0,0,0,,逊爆了这名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.65,0:08:08.65,Default3,,0,0,0,,拙建而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.45,0:08:14.41,Default3,,0,0,0,,唱一些有点色色歌词的歌曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.41,0:08:16.12,Default3,,0,0,0,,用合唱炒热气氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.12,0:08:17.87,Default3,,0,0,0,,女生脱衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.87,0:08:21.87,Default3,,0,0,0,,只要集齐这三点 那这对情侣就一定会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.75,0:08:23.96,Default3,,0,0,0,,这对情侣就会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.42,0:08:27.46,Default3,,0,0,0,,一定会搞起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.75,0:08:28.96,Default3,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.09,0:08:35.13,Default3,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.76,0:08:43.56,Default3,,0,0,0,,卡拉OK是去唱歌的地方啊 才不是啪啪啪的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.56,0:08:45.48,Default3,,0,0,0,,不是...啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.61,Default3,,0,0,0,,喂 撑住啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.52,0:08:52.11,Default3,,0,0,0,,不要辜负我的牺牲 纯一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.32,0:08:53.65,Default3,,0,0,0,,会牺牲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.24,0:08:56.41,Default3,,0,0,0,,去邀请那个辣妹去卡拉OK吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.70,0:08:59.78,Default3,,0,0,0,,这样一来就可以在接吻的同时童贞毕业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.41,0:09:01.33,Default3,,0,0,0,,大概吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.58,0:09:06.92,Default3,,0,0,0,,慎平 慎平!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.92,0:09:08.29,Default3,,0,0,0,,let's kiss
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.46,0:09:14.84,Default3,,0,0,0,,卡拉OK吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.09,0:09:17.55,Default3,,0,0,0,,问题就在于该怎么邀请啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.39,Default3,,0,0,0,,早上好 羽柴君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.76,0:09:21.10,Default3,,0,0,0,,香椎同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.68,0:09:25.02,Default3,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗 一大早就一脸复杂的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.02,0:09:26.44,Default3,,0,0,0,,有什么烦心事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.44,0:09:29.06,Default3,,0,0,0,,没事没事 没什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.06,0:09:30.77,Default3,,0,0,0,,嗯 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.82,0:09:34.03,Default3,,0,0,0,,可以的话 也可以找我商量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.15,0:09:37.20,Default3,,0,0,0,,谢谢 不过真的没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.20,0:09:38.78,Default3,,0,0,0,,谢谢你担心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.95,0:09:43.58,Default3,,0,0,0,,为了跟辣妹啪 而在烦恼怎么邀请她去卡拉OK什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.58,0:09:46.50,Default3,,0,0,0,,我要多厚颜无耻才能找香椎同学谈这种事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.50,0:09:48.25,Default3,,0,0,0,,早安 纯一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.58,0:09:50.38,Default3,,0,0,0,,胸...安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.71,0:09:53.17,Default3,,0,0,0,,好柔软
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.75,0:09:55.84,Default3,,0,0,0,,早上发给你的自拍看了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.84,0:09:57.51,Default3,,0,0,0,,相当兴奋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.80,0:10:00.97,Default3,,0,0,0,,嗯...嗯 很可爱的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.97,0:10:04.22,Default3,,0,0,0,,对吧 我都没用美图哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.72,0:10:06.64,Default3,,0,0,0,,是...吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.85,0:10:11.36,Default3,,0,0,0,,八女同学和羽柴君关系有这么好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.11,0:10:17.45,Default3,,0,0,0,,我和纯一从昨天开始交往了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.41,0:10:22.03,Default3,,0,0,0,,欸!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.67,0:10:31.38,Default3,,0,0,0,,今早真是灾难啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.54,0:10:34.92,Default3,,0,0,0,,还被很多平时都不怎么说话的人搭话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.42,0:10:38.42,Default3,,0,0,0,,根本不是邀请八女同学去卡拉OK的氛围啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.63,0:10:43.47,Default3,,0,0,0,,从早上到现在 八女同学就一直在回答朋友的提问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.47,0:10:45.68,Default3,,0,0,0,,半点搭话的机会都没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.94,Default3,,0,0,0,,等等 我也要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.60,0:10:51.44,Default3,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.60,0:10:52.90,Default3,,0,0,0,,等下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.03,0:11:02.45,Default3,,0,0,0,,你们怎么回事啊 稍微等等我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.49,0:11:07.58,Default3,,0,0,0,,男朋友君你不是有着可爱的女朋友么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.67,Default3,,0,0,0,,应该跟我们这些童贞没什么话好说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.29,0:11:15.00,Default3,,0,0,0,,滚你现充 祝你在痛苦中爆炸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.17,0:11:18.71,Default3,,0,0,0,,纯一 你有问八女同学她有没有妹妹吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.22,0:11:20.76,Default3,,0,0,0,,大家好冷淡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.93,0:11:23.68,Default3,,0,0,0,,我反而是最震惊的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.68,0:11:24.64,Default3,,0,0,0,,烦人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.68,Default3,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道细节 但你实在是太令人羡慕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.68,0:11:31.44,Default3,,0,0,0,,这也太胡扯了 还不是你们强迫我告白的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.44,0:11:33.73,Default3,,0,0,0,,我才不想听大道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.94,0:11:35.27,Default3,,0,0,0,,居然走掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.27,0:11:38.36,Default3,,0,0,0,,真是群自作主张的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.49,0:11:40.36,Default3,,0,0,0,,纯一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.61,0:11:43.61,Default3,,0,0,0,,八女同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.66,Default3,,0,0,0,,纯一 你放学后反正很闲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.95,0:11:49.12,Default3,,0,0,0,,稍微陪我下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.29,0:11:56.46,Default3,,0,0,0,,青蛙啊 回家吧 青蛙啊 回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.30,0:11:59.76,Default3,,0,0,0,,等一下啊 八女同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.26,0:12:02.68,Default3,,0,0,0,,好了 纯一闭嘴跟我来就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.01,0:12:05.64,Default3,,0,0,0,,哥 哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.39,0:12:09.47,Default3,,0,0,0,,宁音?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.48,0:12:14.23,Default3,,0,0,0,,你们为什么牵着手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.52,0:12:15.60,Default3,,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.60,0:12:18.73,Default3,,0,0,0,,我们在交往啊 牵个手很正常吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.36,0:12:26.49,Default3,,0,0,0,,哥哥 你个木脑壳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.16,0:12:29.24,Default3,,0,0,0,,那是纯一的妹妹吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.54,0:12:31.79,Default3,,0,0,0,,小小的好可爱呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.75,0:12:34.79,Default3,,0,0,0,,类似妹妹一样的存在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.17,0:12:38.21,Default3,,0,0,0,,不说了 赶紧走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.04,0:12:40.59,Default3,,0,0,0,,我还没问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.71,Default3,,0,0,0,,这是要去哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.63,0:12:45.51,Default3,,0,0,0,,大声地叫喊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.76,0:12:49.10,Default3,,0,0,0,,而且能够令人身心偷快的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.35,0:12:51.89,Default3,,0,0,0,,这难道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.89,0:12:53.85,Default3,,0,0,0,,两个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.06,0:12:55.02,Default3,,0,0,0,,时间呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.94,0:12:57.73,Default3,,0,0,0,,先一个小时吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.44,0:13:01.28,Default3,,0,0,0,,什么嘛 卡拉OK啊 我还以为是宾馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.61,0:13:02.86,Default3,,0,0,0,,不 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.99,0:13:06.53,Default3,,0,0,0,,她们会拿卡拉OK当宾馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.16,0:13:08.70,Default3,,0,0,0,,和计划一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.03,0:13:10.45,Default3,,0,0,0,,等等 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.45,0:13:14.75,Default3,,0,0,0,,说起来 我只和那三个笨蛋去过卡拉OK啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.96,0:13:18.63,Default3,,0,0,0,,突然就和辣妹来 我到底要唱些什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.63,0:13:21.17,Default3,,0,0,0,,纯一在真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.76,Default3,,0,0,0,,我突然超想唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.76,0:13:26.68,Default3,,0,0,0,,平常的一起来的人却都有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.68,0:13:28.51,Default3,,0,0,0,,原来如此这么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.35,0:13:32.01,Default3,,0,0,0,,本来想和她们一起闹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.52,0:13:35.31,Default3,,0,0,0,,我是替补啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.98,0:13:41.23,Default3,,0,0,0,,今天就暂且用和纯一的校服约会来充数吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.78,0:13:44.28,Default3,,0,0,0,,好 好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.57,0:13:48.86,Default3,,0,0,0,,约会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.86,0:13:52.12,Default3,,0,0,0,,这下就更加不知道该唱什么好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.87,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\c&H000000&\fs40\pos(17,102)\u0}致客人们\N这里是卡拉OK\N请不要做{\c&H141AA5&\u1\s0}K歌以外的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.87,Default3,,0,0,0,,这里是卡拉OK请不要做K歌以外...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.83,Default3,,0,0,0,,这这 这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.17,0:14:01.50,Default3,,0,0,0,,四眼仔说的是真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.13,0:14:09.84,Default3,,0,0,0,,贴了这告知就说明真的有那样的情侣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.34,0:14:11.43,Default3,,0,0,0,,久等啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.14,0:14:15.27,Default3,,0,0,0,,你在学鸡叫吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.27,0:14:16.60,Default3,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.89,0:14:18.23,Default3,,0,0,0,,我拿果汁来了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.64,0:14:19.48,Default3,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.60,0:14:25.28,Default3,,0,0,0,,即便是八女同学也不会跳过接吻直接啪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.28,0:14:27.61,Default3,,0,0,0,,借过一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.45,0:14:35.24,Default3,,0,0,0,,这房间好窄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.04,0:14:37.58,Default3,,0,0,0,,那我先点咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.29,0:14:40.04,Default3,,0,0,0,,刚才是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.04,0:14:41.29,Default3,,0,0,0,,故意的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.29,0:14:42.75,Default3,,0,0,0,,她是在撩我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.92,0:14:45.38,Default3,,0,0,0,,八女同学的体温透过我的手臂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.38,0:14:47.59,Default3,,0,0,0,,我直接能感受到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.80,Default3,,0,0,0,,这下不会真的有戏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.47,Default3,,0,0,0,,八女同学 你要干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.48,Default3,,0,0,0,,我蹭 我磨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.81,0:15:05.19,Default3,,0,0,0,,纯一你已经硬邦邦了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.32,0:15:07.15,Default3,,0,0,0,,这不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.53,0:15:10.70,Default3,,0,0,0,,不放松点的话 可唱不了歌哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.91,0:15:13.70,Default3,,0,0,0,,这状态怎么能唱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.03,0:15:15.70,Default3,,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.58,0:15:17.66,Default3,,0,0,0,,啊 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.58,0:15:24.88,Default3,,0,0,0,,那我来给你按摩 放 松 一 下 吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.13,0:15:28.71,Default3,,0,0,0,,摸麦的手好撩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.01,0:15:35.05,Default3,,0,0,0,,我想多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.60,0:15:37.35,Default3,,0,0,0,,看八女同学就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.72,0:15:42.10,Default3,,0,0,0,,唱的那么欢 纯碎就是来唱歌的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.37,0:16:05.42,Default3,,0,0,0,,纯一你不点歌吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.92,Default3,,0,0,0,,我还在想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.92,0:16:09.71,Default3,,0,0,0,,八女同学你先点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.76,Default3,,0,0,0,,是吗 了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.34,0:16:16.51,Default3,,0,0,0,,这下不妙了 我也得唱两首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.93,0:16:20.85,Default3,,0,0,0,,排行榜上的歌没首认识的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.10,0:16:23.48,Default3,,0,0,0,,我能唱的全都是动漫歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.48,0:16:26.19,Default3,,0,0,0,,完全不知道辣妹喜欢的歌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.81,0:16:30.28,Default3,,0,0,0,,这样的话 我只能唱不太像动漫歇的动漫歌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.28,0:16:37.05,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}我也想要啊 已经无法忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.05,0:16:41.65,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}「不是和谁都可以」这不是借口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.65,0:16:48.15,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}犯错的记忆 这噪音缠绕在耳边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.65,0:16:54.15,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}在我的身体印上你的印记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.15,0:17:00.15,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}我已不想再过没有你的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.21,0:17:01.60,Default3,,0,0,0,,这 这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.60,0:17:06.85,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an7}唱一些有点色色歌词的歌曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.68,Default3,,0,0,0,,我冷静点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.85,0:17:07.10,Default3,,0,0,0,,应该没有别的深意 大概吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.36,0:17:10.98,Default3,,0,0,0,,一直都是我在唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.98,0:17:12.53,Default3,,0,0,0,,纯一你也点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.74,0:17:14.15,Default3,,0,0,0,,嗯 也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.15,0:17:15.49,Default3,,0,0,0,,要唱哪个呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.74,0:17:20.91,Default3,,0,0,0,,那就唱夏日回忆吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.83,0:17:28.63,Default3,,0,0,0,,这不是动漫歌吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.13,0:17:29.79,Default3,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.09,0:17:32.42,Default3,,0,0,0,,一起唱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.84,0:17:35.55,Default3,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.16,0:18:02.83,Default3,,0,0,0,,这动画真的超怀念啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.16,0:18:05.50,Default3,,0,0,0,,是啊 但是好意外啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.66,Default3,,0,0,0,,八女同学居然会唱动漫歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.83,0:18:12.34,Default3,,0,0,0,,这有什么意外的 这首歌在我们这代是必点的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.71,0:18:16.76,Default3,,0,0,0,,我还是挺懂动漫歌的 纯一你使劲点歌就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.55,0:18:20.47,Default3,,0,0,0,,阿嘞 难道说 八女同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.55,0:18:23.22,Default3,,0,0,0,,是在迁就我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.18,0:18:28.35,Default3,,0,0,0,,我们再来一首吧 这首你会么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.02,0:18:29.98,Default3,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.36,0:18:32.90,Default3,,0,0,0,,这个情况不就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.98,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an7}用合唱炒热气氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.98,Default3,,0,0,0,,小一小一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.44,Default3,,0,0,0,,不不不不不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.44,0:18:40.53,Default3,,0,0,0,,怎么能把八女同学的好意套上这么下三滥的法则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.53,0:18:41.87,Default3,,0,0,0,,还是人吗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.87,0:18:43.87,Default3,,0,0,0,,我说 不觉得热么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.24,0:18:44.99,Default3,,0,0,0,,脱啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.50,0:18:53.25,Default3,,0,0,0,,好厉害 全部点亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.38,0:18:56.55,Default3,,0,0,0,,这下只有上了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.71,0:18:59.01,Default3,,0,0,0,,喂 你们冷静点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.17,0:19:02.26,Default3,,0,0,0,,这些只是那个鬼畜眼镜的一面之词吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.26,0:19:03.60,Default3,,0,0,0,,GO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.60,0:19:06.64,Default3,,0,0,0,,也对哦 再怎么说在这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.23,0:19:15.19,Default3,,0,0,0,,喂喂 所以你们才会是童贞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.52,0:19:18.24,Default3,,0,0,0,,还要再给淑女蒙羞吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.86,0:19:21.36,Default3,,0,0,0,,你是 帅哥!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.03,0:19:24.74,Default3,,0,0,0,,八女同学她已经完全绽放了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.03,0:19:28.33,Default3,,0,0,0,,成为了名为欲望的真红蔷薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.54,0:19:31.17,Default3,,0,0,0,,此时不出手还算什么男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.87,0:19:35.21,Default3,,0,0,0,,明哲保身可能会让男人出局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.59,0:19:40.42,Default3,,0,0,0,,根据情况牺牲自己来回应女性才是真男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.88,0:19:41.59,Default3,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.18,0:19:47.26,Default3,,0,0,0,,话说本来就没打算当真男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.39,0:19:52.69,Default3,,0,0,0,,而且即使男人一回也不是绝对能童贞毕业不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.02,0:19:57.15,Default3,,0,0,0,,要是八女向学她没那个意思的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.44,0:19:58.61,Default3,,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.19,0:20:04.24,Default3,,0,0,0,,果然只有举起祖传的求爱标志的宝剑奋勇向前了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.91,0:20:10.37,Default3,,0,0,0,,遵循自己下半身的行为我不会否定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.75,0:20:14.21,Default3,,0,0,0,,但是满足肉欲之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.88,0:20:17.50,Default3,,0,0,0,,对淑女还必须要做一件事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.75,0:20:19.38,Default3,,0,0,0,,是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.26,0:20:24.18,Default3,,0,0,0,,那当然 只能是火热的吻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.76,0:20:29.18,Default3,,0,0,0,,忽略前戏的人是都是远远算不上男人的人渣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.89,0:20:33.60,Default3,,0,0,0,,我们是不想成为这样的人渣的 对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.52,0:20:38.32,Default3,,0,0,0,,热吻 亲嘴 接吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.52,0:20:38.32,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}帅哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.32,0:20:41.28,Default3,,0,0,0,,八女同学 非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.53,0:20:44.99,Default3,,0,0,0,,一直没想到你邀请我来卡拉OK是这个打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.86,0:20:46.62,Default3,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.04,0:20:54.25,Default3,,0,0,0,,这不上的话 不是男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.62,0:20:55.58,Default3,,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.17,0:20:57.67,Default3,,0,0,0,,你鼻毛露出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.59,0:20:59.38,Default3,,0,0,0,,鼻...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.71,0:21:03.88,Default3,,0,0,0,,帅哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.26,0:21:06.22,Default3,,0,0,0,,我稍微去下厉厕所哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.85,0:21:17.56,Default3,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 接吻的目的太明显了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.06,0:21:22.23,Default3,,0,0,0,,怎么可能...那么轻易地就接吻啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.20,0:21:29.32,Default3,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.53,0:21:33.58,Default3,,0,0,0,,以后无论做什么都会被提到「你鼻毛露出来了」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.70,0:21:38.54,Default3,,0,0,0,,可恶 鼻毛 要是没有你的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.67,0:21:43.09,Default3,,0,0,0,,八女同学 请原谅这样鼻孔杂草丛生的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.63,0:21:45.13,Default3,,0,0,0,,今到很开心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.05,0:21:49.51,Default3,,0,0,0,,我可能还想和纯一去卡拉OK呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.93,0:21:53.18,Default3,,0,0,0,,八女同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.52,0:21:55.98,Default3,,0,0,0,,好了 走了啦 快站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.73,0:21:59.35,Default3,,0,0,0,,八女同学 等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.52,0:22:00.36,Default3,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.36,0:22:02.11,Default3,,0,0,0,,怎么鼻孔有点疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.66,0:23:36.99,Default3,,0,0,0,,大伙好 我是步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.99,0:23:37.74,Default3,,0,0,0,,我是心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.74,0:23:40.08,Default3,,0,0,0,,之前心科普了些小知识所以今天该我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.08,0:23:41.16,Default3,,0,0,0,,欸 让我听听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.16,0:23:44.75,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an7)\fs35}卡拉OK:日文ラオケ 其中カオ是空的意思\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hオケ是orchestra(管弦乐)的缩略音译 意为不带歌手(原唱)的管弦乐(伴奏)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.16,0:23:42.58,Default3,,0,0,0,,知道为什么卡拉OK叫卡拉OK吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.58,0:23:44.75,Default3,,0,0,0,,是空的和管弦乐的简称对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.88,0:23:46.84,Default3,,0,0,0,,那么小知识什么时候告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.84,0:23:48.30,Default3,,0,0,0,,你是故意的吗!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.00,0:23:49.51,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(635,530)\fad(300,0)}下回\N第一次的黑GAL
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.30,0:23:49.51,Default3,,0,0,0,,你说的小知识呢?
Comment: Marked=0,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.88,Default3,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.00,0:02:13.48,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Like  自由なキミが好きだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.00,0:02:13.48,Default3,,0,0,0,,Like  虽然喜欢自由的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.68,0:02:18.88,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ほっとかれたらそれはそれでさみしい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.68,0:02:18.88,Default3,,0,0,0,,但如果被冷落的话我会感到寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.46,0:02:23.88,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Love 「髪を切りすぎちゃったみたい」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.56,0:02:23.88,Default3,,0,0,0,,Love 「头发好像剪得太短了」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.08,0:02:25.88,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「ほんとだ」じゃない!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.08,0:02:25.88,Default3,,0,0,0,,你不该说「是真的呢」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.92,0:02:29.24,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}そこは「でもかわいい」でしょ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.92,0:02:29.24,Default3,,0,0,0,,而是要说「剪短也可爱呀」对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.44,0:02:33.05,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}そっと目を閉じたまま
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.44,0:02:33.05,Default3,,0,0,0,,静静闭上眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.05,0:02:35.50,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}指先で探した
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.05,0:02:35.50,Default3,,0,0,0,,用指尖去触及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.50,0:02:40.16,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}鍵と鍵穴みたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.50,0:02:40.16,Default3,,0,0,0,,如钥匙和锁孔般默契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.04,0:02:43.63,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}そうだ この次のデート
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.04,0:02:43.63,Default3,,0,0,0,,下次的约会地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.63,0:02:45.64,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}わたしにまかせて!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.63,0:02:45.64,Default3,,0,0,0,,让我来做决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.00,0:02:50.63,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}夏をプロデュースしたげる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.00,0:02:50.63,Default3,,0,0,0,,这个夏天制造最完美的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.63,0:02:52.60,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ふたりきりで
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.63,0:02:52.60,Default3,,0,0,0,,只有我们在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.83,0:02:53.92,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You are the First One!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.83,0:02:53.92,Default3,,0,0,0,,你是第一个!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.92,0:02:54.41,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.92,0:02:54.41,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.99,0:02:57.76,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ついにやってきましたマブしいSEASON
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.99,0:02:57.76,Default3,,0,0,0,,闪耀的季节终于来临了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.00,0:02:59.43,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an9}yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.00,0:02:59.43,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an3}yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.84,0:02:59.15,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}熱い太陽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.84,0:02:59.15,Default3,,0,0,0,,炎热的太阳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.15,0:03:02.92,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}恋する気持ち もっと盛り上がってゆこう!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.15,0:03:02.92,Default3,,0,0,0,,恋爱的心情让我们再热情高涨一点吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.96,0:03:04.24,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}こたえならYes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.96,0:03:04.24,Default3,,0,0,0,,回答自然是Yes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.24,0:03:04.98,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an9}yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.24,0:03:04.98,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an3}yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.28,0:03:08.12,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}だけどカンタンだって思われたくない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.28,0:03:08.12,Default3,,0,0,0,,但我并不想被人认为太容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.16,0:03:12.72,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}はじめては 一度だけ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.16,0:03:12.72,Default3,,0,0,0,,第一次只有一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.80,0:03:15.88,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}大切に to you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.80,0:03:15.88,Default3,,0,0,0,,我要将自己完整地托付于你
Comment: Marked=0,0:03:14.78,0:03:16.78,Default3,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.60,0:22:13.32,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ヘナチョコ面に见せかけ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.60,0:22:13.32,Default3,,0,0,0,,故意装成无能的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.32,0:22:15.88,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}案外やるときゃやる奴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.32,0:22:15.88,Default3,,0,0,0,,意外的是个可靠的家伙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.92,0:22:18.66,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}それでもちょこっと
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.92,0:22:18.66,Default3,,0,0,0,,却又总是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.66,0:22:21.16,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}褒めれば调子に乗ってドジる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.66,0:22:21.16,Default3,,0,0,0,,给点阳光就得意忘形弄巧成拙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.28,0:22:24.34,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ズタボロ破れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.28,0:22:24.34,Default3,,0,0,0,,撕裂纵横的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.34,0:22:26.45,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}恋の伤痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.34,0:22:26.45,Default3,,0,0,0,,恋爱的伤痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.45,0:22:31.28,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}谁にも一生见せたくないけれど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.45,0:22:31.28,Default3,,0,0,0,,明明谁都不愿意见到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.12,0:22:37.40,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}なぜだろ自然と会话してる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.12,0:22:37.40,Default3,,0,0,0,,为什么又情不自禁地说起了话呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.84,0:22:40.36,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}なんだろな この感覚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.84,0:22:40.36,Default3,,0,0,0,,是什么呢 这种感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.44,0:22:43.20,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}あたたかい この安らぎ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.44,0:22:43.20,Default3,,0,0,0,,好温暖 感到安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.20,0:22:45.60,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}なんてことナイナイ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.20,0:22:45.60,Default3,,0,0,0,,什么的才没有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.60,0:22:48.10,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}人生は甘くない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.60,0:22:48.10,Default3,,0,0,0,,人生可不甜美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.20,0:22:53.40,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}さあ 跪きなさい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.20,0:22:53.40,Default3,,0,0,0,,来 跪下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.80,0:22:56.25,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}あたしが好きならば!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.80,0:22:56.25,Default3,,0,0,0,,要是喜欢我的话!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.25,0:22:57.74,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}本気でね 本気でね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.25,0:22:57.74,Default3,,0,0,0,,真的哦 真的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.74,0:23:00.70,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ハート射止めようとか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.74,0:23:00.70,Default3,,0,0,0,,想得到我的心什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.70,0:23:01.95,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}100年早い
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.70,0:23:01.95,Default3,,0,0,0,,还早100年呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.95,0:23:03.08,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ほんとはね ほんとはね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.95,0:23:03.08,Default3,,0,0,0,,其实啊 其实啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.08,0:23:04.25,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}うざい程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.08,0:23:04.25,Default3,,0,0,0,,你真是个麻烦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.25,0:23:06.80,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}良いやつなんだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.25,0:23:06.80,Default3,,0,0,0,,不错的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.80,0:23:07.25,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.80,0:23:07.25,Default3,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.25,0:23:08.34,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}本気でね 本気でね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.25,0:23:08.34,Default3,,0,0,0,,真的哦 真的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.34,0:23:11.45,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}とことん叱られても
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.34,0:23:11.45,Default3,,0,0,0,,再怎么呵斥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.45,0:23:12.45,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}惩りないとこ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.45,0:23:12.45,Default3,,0,0,0,,也不会退缩这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.45,0:23:13.73,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ほんとわね ほんとわね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.45,0:23:13.73,Default3,,0,0,0,,其实啊 其实啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.73,0:23:17.93,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}かわいいなんて 思えちゃう
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.73,0:23:17.93,Default3,,0,0,0,,很可爱什么的 一不小心就这么觉得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.18,0:23:20.40,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}あれはヤダ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.18,0:23:20.40,Default3,,0,0,0,,那样不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.40,0:23:21.60,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}それもダメ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.40,0:23:21.60,Default3,,0,0,0,,那样也不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.60,0:23:24.35,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}わがままじゃないんだわ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.60,0:23:24.35,Default3,,0,0,0,,可不是我任性哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.35,0:23:27.05,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}あたしだけ 见てなさい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.35,0:23:27.05,Default3,,0,0,0,,请只注视着 我一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.05,0:23:32.80,Default3,,0,0,0,,{\an8}こう见えて 寂しがりやだし
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.05,0:23:32.80,Default3,,0,0,0,,别看是这样 其实是个害怕寂寞的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.51,0:23:56.51,Default3,,0,0,0,,
